item.dc:creator: @cloudscape cloudscape
item.description:
@cloudscape wrote:

[quote=“Rastafarai, post:32, topic:244634”]can u say again how its named ?
and what to look there exactly ?[/quote]

Seeing as you are using notepad… press CTRL+F and type “PK PK PK” into the pop up search bar. Then change all the “PK PK PK” to “Villagescape”.
Then search it again just to double check you did it all, then close the notepad and save it, next open up your server folder and find compile.bat and run it. (post any errors back here) then find run.bat in your server files and run. then it should all be up to date.

Thanks for your time.
